            <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><p><seg rend="left"><pb facs="NLJ0007.tif"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date>9.&#160;11.&#160;08</date></seg></p><p><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb133" type="place">Wien XVIII. Spoettelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></p><salute>werther Herr Ehrenſtein,</salute></opener><p>we<c rendition="#gemination-n"/> Sie <date>Freitag</date> etwa <time>½&#160;7 Abend</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL935-1"/>Zeit haben<note type="commentary" xml:id="KL935-1h">Er hatte Zeit, das Treffen fand
                am <date>13.&#160;11.&#160;1908</date> statt.</note>, ſo ſind Sie 
                    willko<c rendition="#gemination-m"/>en Ihrem</p><closer>ergeb<unclear>enen</unclear><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><signed>A.&#160;S.</signed></closer></div>
